## 运行方式

### 环境变量（必须）

```bash
export SGLANG_ENABLE_JIT_DEEPGEMM=0
```

### 离线推理

```bash
cd /root/paddlejob/workspace/env_run/output/t2i_comfy/baidu/personal-code/sglang-ernie-image

SGLANG_ENABLE_JIT_DEEPGEMM=0 sglang generate \
    --model-path /root/paddlejob/workspace/env_run/output/diffusers_version/safetensors \
    --prompt "一只可爱的橙色小猫坐在窗台上" \
    --height 1024 --width 1024 \
    --num-inference-steps 50 \
    --guidance-scale 5.0 \
    --seed 42 \
    --output-path ./outputs/
```

### 独立脚本推理

```bash
python scripts/inference_ernie_image.py \
    --prompt "一只可爱的橙色小猫坐在窗台上" \
    --output test_output.png \
    --height 1024 --width 1024 \
    --steps 30 --guidance-scale 5.0 --seed 42
```

### HTTP 服务

```bash
SGLANG_ENABLE_JIT_DEEPGEMM=0 sglang serve \
    --model-path /root/paddlejob/workspace/env_run/output/diffusers_version/safetensors \
    --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8800 --num-gpus 1
```

### 请求

```bash
curl http://localhost:30000/v1/images/generations   -H "Content-Type: application/json"   -d '{
    "prompt": "一只可爱的橙色小猫",
    "size": "1024x1024",
    "num_inference_steps": 30,
    "guidance_scale": 5.0,
    "seed": 42,
    "response_format": "b64_json"
  }'
```

